<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/969499-does-anyone-of-true-intellect-really">Does anyone of true intellect really believe that reading a book of fiction, like this one, really advances one&#39;s values? Or one&#39;s life? No. It is silly fiction. It never happened nor would it ever. It is of no use to us. At all.</a>
</div>
