<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Does anyone of true intellect really believe that spending their time putting down and complaining about others, like Geoffrey Jones, really advances <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Does anyone of true intellect really believe that spending their time putting down and complaining about others, like Geoffrey Jones, really advances one's values? Or one's life? No. It is a silly waste of time. But here it is. It is of no use to us. At all. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
