<span id="freeTextContainer13866358429246403818">Someone please give me the power to finish trudging through this book. Interesting idea &amp; setting, but the writing is T.E.D.I.O.U.S.<br/>I love nice descriptive writing as much as the next reader, but this is kind of ridiculous.</span>

